definition: to arrange/to line up/file/series/(in data tables) column/(Tw) row
to enter/to go into/to join/to become a member of/to confirm or agree with/abbr. for 入聲|入声[ru4 sheng1]

sentences.english: But he seemed to only include ten letters in his list.
sentences.chinese: 他似乎只把十封信列入了他的清单里。

sentences.english: It is necessary and appropriate that the interest should he listed into the standard system of the text compiling.
sentences.chinese: 将趣味性列入课文编选的标准体系是必要的和适宜的。

sentences.english: So why is the humble chair being blacklisted?
sentences.chinese: 但为什么这次是“老实巴交”的椅子被列入黑名单呢？

sentences.english: Dazu Rock Carvings in 1999 was inscribed on the World Heritage List.
sentences.chinese: 大足石刻1999年被列入世界文化遗产名录。

sentences.english: Yet according to Cox, yttrium was not even listed in the report.
sentences.chinese: 但根据考克斯的说法，钇甚至没被列入这份报告之中。

sentences.english: However, only the wrong routing alarm was included on the short-list.
sentences.chinese: 然而，只有错误的路由警报是列入名单。

sentences.english: He's been wait-listed for a football scholarship to Stanford .
sentences.chinese: 他已被列入斯坦福大学的美式足球奖学金等候者名单。

sentences.english: And this president has even approved names of American citizens on that list.
sentences.chinese: 而且这个大总统甚至把一些美国公民也列入名单。

sentences.english: That’s why Wikipedia is an ideal candidate to set the World Heritage List right.
sentences.chinese: 这就是为什么维基百科被题名列入世界遗产之列。

sentences.english: Osteoma should be included in the differential diagnosis of calcified masses in cerebellopontine angle.
sentences.chinese: 在小脑桥脑角之钙化肿块，骨瘤必须列入鉴别诊断。

sentences.english: This section has been removed from Listing 2 to simplify the explanation.
sentences.chinese: 为了减化说明，此部分没有列入清单2中。

sentences.english: But you don't plan to snack, so you overeat.
sentences.chinese: 但是你并没把吃零食列入计划，所以你会吃得过量。

sentences.english: They were blacklisted because of their extreme right-wing views.
sentences.chinese: 他们因极右观点而被列入黑名单。

sentences.english: I think she has been shortlisted for the Booker prize this year.
sentences.chinese: 我想她已经被列入今年“布克奖”的终选名单了。

sentences.english: Iron comes under"Metals" in the list.
sentences.chinese: 铁在此单中列入“金属”栏下。
